🧠 The Logic Behind the Project
As an aspiring MERN Stack Developer, my philosophy is Logic Building > Frameworks.

In this project, I moved away from "Tutorial Hell" to build custom logic for:
Data Normalization: Handling empty inputs and preventing duplicate tasks.
State Management: Syncing the UI with the underlying data array in real-time.
UI Feedback: Managing asynchronous timers for status messages to avoid UI flickering.

